## 10. Quick Reference

| Task | Command |
|---|---|
| Check status | `git status` |
| Commit history | `git log --oneline --graph` |
| See changes | `git diff` |
| Undo unstaged changes | `git restore <file>` |
| Unstage a file | `git restore --staged <file>` |
| Stash work in progress | `git stash` / `git stash pop` |
| Sync fork with upstream | `git fetch upstream && git merge upstream/main` |
| List tracked files | `git ls-files` |

